<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77681fc5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410aaa–55"><num value="410aaa–55">§ 410aaa–55.</num><heading> Construction of visitor center</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to construct a visitor center in the preserve for the purpose of providing information through appropriate displays, printed material, and other interpretive programs, about the resources of the preserve.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77681fc6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/433/tV/s515">Pub. L. 103–433, title V, § 515</ref>, <date date="1994-10-31">Oct. 31, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/4494">108 Stat. 4494</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
